entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: For better or worse the poison in the hands of Tori and Jabba. Maybe it will only be used against other criminal elements, but somehow you imagine that's not a realistic belief.
entries.journal_entry_description: Jabba is always looking for an edge. He's surrounded by the most backstabbing and efficient killers in the galaxy. If he doesn't have an angle, a piece of information that can beat any one of them to the draw, then he is dead. Jabba has been in the business for a long time and he plans to stay there. Something like a new poison is just the kind of edge Jabba wants.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Go to the Cult of the Krayt cave and collect six poison glands from Bone Gnashers.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Collect 6 Poison Glands from Bone Gnashers
entries.task02_comm_message_text: Heh, heh. You were lucky to get through those cultists. Make sure you return those poison glands to Tori, and then report back to Reimos.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Return to Tori with the poison glands.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Good Work! You have completed the Bone Gnasher quest.
